headline: BofA Stays Constructive on Cisco (CSCO) with Price Target Raised to $85
summary: Cisco Systems Inc. (NASDAQ:CSCO) is one of the best data center stocks to buy now. On August 14, BofA analyst Tal Liani raised his price target on Cisco Systems Inc. (NASDAQ:CSCO) to $85 from $76 while maintaining a Buy rating. The analyst believes that Cisco’s Q4 results and FY 2026 guidance were modestly better than expected, […]
